	[em 
		"Sonic VR
	]em
	" is a ROM hack of 
	[em 
		"Sonic the Hedgehog 2
	]em
	" by ColinC10. It features a series of short virtual reality-styled levels where the goal is to get to the finish ring as fast as you can without dying. There are no power-ups, rings, or time limit to assist or hold back Sonic. The only thing that serves as a challenge are the 
	[em 
		"Sonic
	]em
	" physics mechanics, which are remarkably different from the physics in other platforming games made at the time.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/marzojr 
		"marzojr
	]a
	" here completes all 40 levels as fast as possible, exploiting bugs and quirks in the 
	[em 
		"Sonic
	]em
	" engine to clip through walls and not take damage from hitting certain hazards.
	$LF
